        "when": "2021-11",
        "text": "Toni did a truly incredible job with our photos. I surprised my Fiancee with our engagement, and Toni was there to capture the moment beautifully. Her photography style is amazing and she definitely stood out to me out of all of the other photographers I looked at in the area. She is incredibly professional and easy to work with. Fast turn around time on edits and great communication. Highly recommend!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-01",
        "text": "I highly recommend Toni Axelrod. Toni is extremely professional, great to work with, and takes incredible photos. I surprised my now fiancé with a proposal in Vail, and Toni helped me pick the perfect spot and captured the moment beautifully. I emailed Toni two weeks before my planned proposal, and she was quick to respond with a call. Toni had amazing ideas to help me decide on how I wanted to propose. On the day of the proposal, Toni had excellent communication to help the surprise go smoothly. Toni has a great personality and made the photo shoot so much fun! She took her time, and made sure that we got every photo that we wanted. She was very quick to edit the photos and get them back to us to share with our family. 10/10 would recommend Toni!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-02",
        "text": "If I could give Toni 10 stars, I would. She took our engagement photos one year ago, and so when we knew that we were going to head back to Vail for our wedding, we just had to work with her again. She was so fun to be around, accommodated our last-minute schedule, and the pictures turned out absolutely stunning."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-02",
        "text": "Toni Axelrod Studios is absolutely incredible! Toni captured both our engagement and wedding beautifully, and we couldn't be happier with the results. She has an amazing eye for photography, and it truly shows in every shot. Not only is her work stunning, but she is also so easy to work with professional, personable, and genuinely passionate about what she does. She made both experiences seamless and fun, allowing us to fully enjoy these once-in-a-lifetime moments. If you're looking for a photographer who will exceed your expectations, Toni is the one! Highly recommend!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2024-04",
        "text": "Toni provided excellent service at our private event at the Vail Whiskey Distillery for our business VIP clients. In the course of our ongoing conversations via e-mail and Zoom, she was able to understand all our needs in a broad way and brought up ideas based on her experience. We were able to give our clients the wow effect after she set up the location and printed the photos on the spot. We were very pleased with Toni's prompt arrival, her responsiveness, pleasant demeanor, and the impressive products she provided.\nWe will definitely work with her in the future!"
